message: The RATIONALE field for indicator 4-3-2, translated into all languages

data.en: The indicator aims to measure the percentage of trainee and student who have achieved the minimum learning outcomes in vocational education program.
data.km: សូចនាករនេះមានគោលបំណងវាស់វែងភាគរយនៃសិក្ខាកាមនិងនិស្សិតដែលទទួលបានលទ្ធផលសិក្សាអប្បបរមានៅក្នុងកម្មវិធីអប់រំវិជ្ជាជីវៈ។
